ActSpecial Economic Measures Act
SubjectSpecial Economic Measures (Ukraine) Permit Authorization Order
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to issue to any person in Canada and any Canadian outside Canada a permit to carry out a specified activity or transaction, or any class of activity or transaction, with a designated person that is otherwise restricted or prohibited pursuant to the SPECIAL ECONOMIC MEASURES (UKRAINE) REGULATIONS.
